 | title=All Praise to thee, my God, this night
 | publisher=Cyberhymnal
 | deadurl=yes
 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101220054521/http://www.hymntime.com/tch/htm/a/l/l/allprais.htm
 | archivedate=2010-12-20
 }}</ref>, [[:en:Thomas_Ken|Thomas Ken]]<BR>
2. [[聽啊!天使高聲唱|聽啊!天使高聲唱]] Hark! The Herald Angels Sing|Hark! The Herald Angels Sing, [[查理·卫斯理|查理·卫斯理]] <BR>
3. 看哪 救主駕雲降臨 [[:en:Charles_Wesley#Best-known_hymns|Lo! He comes with clouds descending]], [[查理·卫斯理|查理·卫斯理]] <BR>
4. 萬古磐石,或永久磐石  [[:en:Rock_of_Ages_(Christian_hymn)|Rock of Ages]], [[:en:Augustus_Montague_Toplady|Augustus Toplady]]

